Dataset Information

Dataset Name: Amazon Video Games Reviews (Amazon Product Data)

Source: Publicly available on Amazon Review Dataset (UCSD / Julian McAuley’s Group)

Amazon Product Review Dataset

Also mirrored on Kaggle: Amazon Video Game Reviews

Data Size in Your Case: 497,240 reviews × 10 columns

Columns Used (after cleaning):

overall → Rating (1–5 stars)

verified → Verified purchase (1/0)

reviewerID → Unique reviewer ID

asin → Product ID

reviewerName → Reviewer name

reviewText → Full review text

summary → Short summary of review

unixReviewTime → Review time (datetime)

vote → Helpful vote count

style → Platform (PC, Xbox, PlayStation, etc.)
